    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>A more raw approach without using sort Arrays.sort method.\nThis is using insertion sort.</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static void main(String[] args){\n    String wordSt=\"watch\";\n    char[] word=wordSt.toCharArray();\n\n    for(int i=0;i&lt;(word.length-1);i++){\n        for(int j=i+1;j&gt;0;j--){\n            if(word[j]&lt;word[j-1]){\n                char temp=word[j-1];\n                word[j-1]=word[j];\n                word[j]=temp;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    wordSt=String.valueOf(word);\n    System.out.println(wordSt);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
